@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.94 - tmp + 0.73) - (tmp + 0.47 * v0 + 0.54)) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.43) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.24)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.93)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(v2))
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = wp.sin(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
